## Vision
Create a complete and maintainable Laravel package that provides reusable Blade UI components and ready-to-use templates based on daisyUI v5 and Tailwind CSS v4.

## Mission
- Provide a library of reusable and well-structured Blade components
- Provide reusable application-facing templates such as auth, profile, notification center, and chat
- Strictly respect daisyUI v5 and Tailwind CSS v4 standards
- Maintain a clean Laravel package architecture with a minimal public surface
- Guarantee compatibility with all Laravel applications

## Priorities
- Code quality and maintainability
- Component consistency and reusability
- Host application integration simplicity
- Security, explicit contracts, and low-coupling package boundaries
